<div id="preface" class="white">
  <div class="row heading">
	<h3>Reflect helps brands power their communications with digital media solutions and immersive guest experiences, engaging their customers from beginning to end.</h3>
  </div>
</div>  
</div>
<div id="block-views-front-solutions-block" class="block block-views">


<div class="view view-front-solutions view-id-front_solutions view-display-id-block view-dom-id-e41fd3c3396f389be6e3e5e6bdc28b31">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
    

<div class="parallax-37 parallax-image" data-stellar-background-ratio="0.5">
	<div class="tint largepadding">
		<!-- section heading -->
		<section class="row heading">
				<h1>DIGITAL BRAND MEDIA</h1>
		</section>
		
		<section class="row heading">
      <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><div class="dots">&nbsp;</div>
<!-- first block -->

<div class="four columns center pull-left">
	<!-- columns info -->

	<h4>PASSIVE DIGITAL<br />MEDIA</h4>

	<p>Passive display solutions utilize HD Media for awareness and motivation. From single displays to video walls and mobile devices, passive digital media is used for promotional messaging, product information, and entertainment. Smart Media controls are utilized for powerful targeting.</p>
</div>
<!-- second block -->

<div class="four columns center">
	<!-- columns info -->

	<h4>INTERACTIVE<br />EXPERIENCES</h4>

	<p>Interactive display systems change the way consumers interact with and connect with your brand.  Interactive media can include passive media branded content and interactive apps, self-service apps and on-demand media, tablet solutions, and mobile integration.</p>
</div>
<!-- third block -->

<div class="four columns center">
	<!-- columns info -->

	<h4>DYNAMIC DIGITAL<br />MEDIA</h4>

	<p>Dynamic digital media utilizes real-time content feeds.  With dynamic digital media, messaging and content changes based on different contexts creating a more live, interactive experience with digital screens. Dynamic content can include weather, sports, news, and more.</p>
</div>
<!-- end four columns --></div></div></div>		</section>
	</div>
</div>  </div>
    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
